INCIPIT grimoire "callback_invoke0_basic"

ADVOCARE "cct/callback.cct"

RITUALE answer() REDDE REX
  REDDE 42
EXPLICIT RITUALE

RITUALE main() REDDE REX
  EVOCA SPECULUM NIHIL fn AD answer
  SI CONIURA callback_invoke0 GENUS(REX)(fn) != 42
    REDDE 10
  FIN SI
  REDDE 0
EXPLICIT RITUALE

EXPLICIT grimoire
